{"tid":1791821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藍大戰大家千其唔好入場支持，會出事","createTime":"2019-12-21T07:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:40:03.000Z","uid":208122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa463056150e03803d43b7ed91dca3385d185a0","tid":1791821,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港超<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>大戰</span></strong></span></span><br />\n香港人撐完港足，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好當港超係CONDOM</span></span></strong>。<br />\n一定要出錢出力入場撐港超，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復足球文化圈</span></strong></span></span><br />\n成日話假日香港冇地方好去冇野好做，依家就同我入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩聽就同我推上去同埋入場睇，淨係需要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">$20</span></strong>就入場睇到<br />\n<br />\n理文對東方龍師 黃藍大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日 12月21日 下午2:30<br />\n深水埗運動場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>$20特惠，$60正常票價</strong></span><br />\n不可預購門票，只限即場購買，球場個半鐘前會開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wurZPYe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwurZPYe.jpg&h=d04927bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48b8879be91fc006339fb5e2937086bf1bbef0f0","tid":1791821,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"想問下點解係黃點解係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990d28b8b79dda73872ef9edc8c0f6b14bc3f76d","tid":1791821,"uid":241543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"48b8879be91fc006339fb5e2937086bf1bbef0f0","tid":1791821,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:20:37.